{
  "name": "AIKAGAN — Omnichannel Router (auto-provisioned, minimal)",
  "flow": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "module": "gateway:CustomWebHook",
      "version": 1,
      "parameters": {
        "hook": "AIKAGAN_OMNI_HOOK",
        "maxResults": 1
      },
      "mapper": {},
      "metadata": {
        "designer": { "x": 0, "y": 0 },
        "restore": { "parameters": { "hook": { "label": "AIKAGAN omni-hook" } } }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "module": "http:ActionSendData",
      "version": 3,
      "parameters": {},
      "mapper": {
        "url": "https://httpbin.org/post",
        "method": "POST",
        "headers": [
          { "name": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
          { "name": "X-AIKAGAN-Source", "value": "omnichannel-archive" }
        ],
        "qs": [],
        "bodyType": "raw",
        "contentType": "application/json",
        "data": "{\"received\":true,\"campaign\":\"{{1.campaign}}\",\"wave\":{{1.wave}}}",
        "useNewZLibDeCompress": true
      },
      "metadata": {
        "designer": { "x": 300, "y": 0 },
        "restore": {
          "parameters": {
            "method": { "label": "POST" },
            "bodyType": { "label": "Raw" },
            "contentType": { "label": "JSON (application/json)" }
          },
          "expect": {
            "method": { "label": "POST" },
            "headers": { "items": [null, null] }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "metadata": {
    "instant": true,
    "version": 1,
    "scenario": {
      "roundtrips": 1,
      "maxErrors": 3,
      "autoCommit": true,
      "autoCommitTriggerLast": true,
      "sequential": false,
      "confidential": false,
      "dataloss": false,
      "dlq": false
    },
    "designer": { "orphans": [] },
    "zone": "eu2.make.com",
    "notes": [
      "MINIMAL provisioning blueprint — only the webhook trigger + a no-op archive POST.",
      "Replace the httpbin.org URL with your own archive endpoint, OR build out the router and platform modules inside the Make.com UI.",
      "For the full router design with all 7 platform paths, import scripts/agent/make_blueprints/omnichannel-router-full.blueprint.json via Make.com → New scenario → Import blueprint (may require manual fix-up if your zone uses different module IDs)."
    ]
  }
}
